  --stdin           Read the task brief, or pack eval JSON with --eval, from standard input
  --route id        Force a route id from `design-ai route --json`
  --with-learning   Include brief-relevant local learning preferences and record local usage metadata
  --learning-category kind  Include only one learning category; requires --with-learning
  --learning-limit N        Limit included learning entries, 1-100; requires --with-learning
  --max-bytes N     Maximum context bytes to include, 1000-1000000. Default: 120000
  --eval-template   Generate a runnable pack eval checkpoint JSON template
  --eval            Run deterministic prompt-pack checkpoint cases
  --strict          With --eval, exit non-zero on warning or failure
  --json            Emit machine-readable bundle
  --out file        Write output to a file instead of stdout
  --force           Overwrite an existing --out file

Environment:
  DESIGN_AI_LEARNING_FILE=/path/learning.json        Override the profile used by --with-learning
  DESIGN_AI_LEARNING_USAGE_FILE=/path/usage.json     Override the local usage sidecar path

Examples:
